  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: General </p><p>Prerequisite: Durable Feat </p><p>You have the blood of heroes flowing through your veins.</p><p> You gain the following benefits: </p><p>• Increase your Constitution score by 1, to a maximum of 20.</p><p>• You must now fail 5 Death saving throws before dying.</p><p>• Whenever you take the Dodge action in combat, you can spend one Hit Die to heal yourself.</p><p> Roll the die, add your Constitution modifier, and regain a number of hit points equal to the total (minimum of one).</p><p>• If you would roll a natural 20 on a Death saving throw, you instead regain a number of hit points equal to your level.</p><p></p>",
